docs.name: Uso - SID (TV Size) [Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood Ending 1] (Cinema)
docs.description:
Poodle and lower V3 Arc diff as usual. Lights are very basic since Cinema is expected to be used (love the ending 1 video).

I wasn't happy with the audio quality of the tv edit mp3 so the map used the full song flac. Which I edited to be similar to the TV sized version. So yes I know its not exactly the same as the ending 1 but close enough.

Love FMA Brotherhood and might do some more in the future.

Thanks for the playtests LassoCatsidy!
